General.Name: Danel (Adir Yeoshua) Ltd
General.Description: Danel (Adir Yeoshua) Ltd provides human resources services in Israel. It offers recruitment, placement, and employment services in the areas of employment, nursing, welfare, and education; and nursing and medical services. The company also operates schools for special education and people with learning disabilities and autism. It serves government ministries, public bodies, the defense industries, and private companies. Danel (Adir Yeoshua) Ltd was incorporated in 1974 and is based in Ramat Gan, Israel.
